        "所有理性投资者都会在这条线上选择自己的组合。"
      ],
      "type": "narration"
    },
    {
      "focus_terms": [],
      "formula": {
        "latex": "E(R_p) = R_f + \\frac{E(R_M) - R_f}{\\sigma_M} \\sigma_p",
